lost_taxa.description: Check that otcetera's tc-taxonomy-parser and otc-unprune-solution-and-name-unnamed-nodes tools agree about the number of taxa that are not present in the solution

lost_taxa_included_in_tree.description: Check that none of the taxa listed as "lost" are in the annotations file

monophyly.description: Check that the taxa from the monophyly tests listed in https://github.com/OpenTreeOfLife/germinator/blob/master/taxa/monophyly.csv are monophyletic in the tree.

num_tips.description: Check that the cleaned version of the taxonomy and the supertree have the same number of leaves

unsupported_nodes.description: Check that none of the nodes listed in the annotations file are completely unsuported
